Read the README.md to understand the project purpose.
When asked to modify modes, look into the modes directory and only modify the .md file.
Don't modify too much, only the necessary parts.
A mode usually has a workflow and a behavior.
Focus on the workflow if asked to modify the workflow and dont change the behavior.
Focus on the behavior if asked to modify the behavior and dont change the workflow.

If you want to understand how modes are structured, read the README_MODES.md file.

If you want to understand the workflow and handover of the modes, read the /project/README.md file.
